nearly a factor of two, extending the bandpass to cover 360 nm {\textless}$\lambda$ {\textless}1000 nm, and increasing the number of fibers from 640 to
1000 per exposure. In this paper we describe the original SDSS
spectrograph design and the upgrades implemented for BOSS, and document
the predicted and measured performances.},
